@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.sin(v0))
    v0 = 0.60
    v2 = (wp.abs(v2) * 0.74)
    v0 = (0.28 * wp.sin((v1 + 0.98 + v0 + 0.42)))
    v1 = wp.exp(v1)
    data[tid] = v0
